OL,5,Carrest kick
OL,7,FA police officer filmed kicking a man
OL,8,Fin the head after he had been brought
OL,9,Fdown with a Taser could still face
OL,10,Fmisconduct charges - as a man is found
OL,11,Fguilty of assaulting his female
OL,12,Fcolleagues.
OL,14,FPC Zachary Marsden is being
OL,15,Finvestigated by the police complaints
OL,16,Fwatchdog over allegations of
OL,17,Fprofessional misconduct towards
OL,18,FMohammed Fahir Amaaz, 20, following an
OL,19,Fincident at Manchester Airport in July
OL,20,F2024.
