OL,4,Cinvestigation for misconduct following
OL,5,Carrest kick
OL,7,FIt comes as Amaaz was convicted of the
OL,8,Fassaults of PC Lydia Ward and PC Ellie
OL,9,FCook after a fracas broke out while
OL,10,Fthe officers attempted to arrest him.
OL,12,FMobile phone footage of the aftermath
OL,13,Fof the arrest went viral on social
OL,14,Fmedia after it showed the Greater
OL,15,FManchester Police (GMP) officer
OL,16,Fkicking Amaaz while he lying was on
OL,17,Fthe floor.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
