OL,4,Cinvestigation for misconduct following
OL,5,Carrest kick
OL,7,FIt sparked protests in the brothers'
OL,8,Fhometown of Rochdale and Manchester
OL,9,Fcity centre, as campaigners took to
OL,10,Fthe streets against "police brutality
OL,11,Fof a Muslim family".
OL,13,FWithin hours of the video emerging the
OL,14,Fbrothers appeared in another video
OL,15,Fwith their solicitor - who described
OL,16,Fthem as traumatised.
OL,18,FSpeaking at the time, Dal Babu, the
OL,19,Fformer Chief Superintendent at the
OL,20,FMetropolitan Police, said he was
OL,21,F"incredibly shocked" by the footage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
