OL,3,CAirport officer still under
OL,4,Cinvestigation for misconduct following
OL,5,Carrest kick
OL,7,F"They should have suspended the
OL,8,Fofficer immediately, they (GMP) have
OL,9,Fbeen brought effectively kicking and
OL,10,Fscreaming to do what the community
OL,11,Fwants it to do," he said.
OL,13,F"I was incredibly shocked by the
OL,14,Fbrutality and the level of violence
OL,15,Fused by the police officer which was
OL,16,Fnot proportionate or necessary."
OL,18,FPC Marsden was swiftly suspended by
OL,19,FGMP and he was placed under criminal
OL,20,Finvestigation for assault.
