OL,5,Carrest kick
OL,7,FBut, shortly after, Greater Manchester
OL,8,FMayor Andy Burnham said it was not as
OL,9,F"clear cut" as many believed the
OL,10,Ffootage made it out to be.
OL,12,F"We would never be so complacent as to
OL,13,Fsay there are no issues with
OL,14,Fdiscrimination in parts of our police
OL,15,Fforce or other police forces, you have
OL,16,Falways got to be very challenging on
OL,17,Fthat front - and we are.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
