OL,7,F"But in this instance it is a
OL,8,Fcomplicated situation I think it is a
OL,9,Fcomplicated situation, it is not as
OL,10,Fclear cut."
OL,12,FHe added: "It's not for any of us just
OL,13,Fto rush to judgement and say they know
OL,14,Feverything off the back of something
OL,15,Foff social media.
OL,17,F"The right thing to do is to have a
OL,18,Fprocess of investigation that is as
OL,19,Findependent as it can be."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/16
