OL,7,FIn a press conference the brothers
OL,8,Fclaimed they were the victims of a
OL,9,Fsmear campaign and also alleged their
OL,10,Fmother was left badly bruised after
OL,11,Fbeing hit in the face with a taser
OL,12,Fduring the incident.
OL,14,FTheir solicitor, Aamer Anwar, told the
OL,15,Fmedia: "The two young men sat here
OL,16,Ftoday, along with their mother family,
OL,17,Fare left devastated and traumatised by
OL,18,Fthe incident at Manchester Airport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
