OL,7,F"Despite the clear attempt by some to
OL,8,Fplace disinformation in the media and
OL,9,Fon social media, the young men sat
OL,10,Fnext to me do not have a single
OL,11,Fcriminal conviction, not even a
OL,12,Fspeeding ticket."
OL,14,FFive months later, after a file was
OL,15,Fsent to the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,16,Fby the Independent Office of Police
OL,17,FConduct (IOPC), the body decided PC
OL,18,FMarsden would not be charged with any
OL,19,Fcriminal offence, while Amaaz and his
OL,20,Fbrother would face assault charges.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/16
