OL,7,FDespite the CPS's decision, the IOPC
OL,8,Fsay its investigation has not
OL,9,Fconcluded as the watchdog is still to
OL,10,Fmake a decision on if there is case
OL,11,Ffor misconduct.
OL,13,FIt said it would take into account all
OL,14,Fevidence gathered during the
OL,15,Finvestigation - including anything
OL,16,Frelevant from the trial.
