OL,7,F"Our independent investigation into
OL,8,Fthe use of force by Greater Manchester
OL,9,FPolice (GMP) officers on six people
OL,10,Fduring a series of arrests at
OL,11,FManchester Airport on 23 July 2024 is
OL,12,Fnearing completion," a spokesperson
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"At the end of the investigation, we
OL,16,Fare required to determine whether
OL,17,Fthere is an indication that anyone
OL,18,Fserving with the police may have
OL,19,Fbreached the standards of professional
OL,20,Fbehaviour.
