OL,7,F"This will take into account all of
OL,8,Fthe evidence gathered during the
OL,9,Finvestigation, not simply matters that
OL,10,Fwere under criminal investigation.
OL,12,F"On concluding our investigation, we
OL,13,Fwill inform the officers, GMP and the
OL,14,Fpeople involved in the arrests of our
OL,15,Finitial determinations."
