OL,7,FDuring the four week criminal trial
OL,8,Fagainst the brothers CCTV from the
OL,9,Fairport, played in court, revealed the
OL,10,Fmoments before the viral footage,
OL,11,Fwhich saw Amaaz land 10 punches and
OL,12,Fkicks on officers.
OL,14,FBoth brothers denied the allegations
OL,15,Fand claimed they acted in self defence
OL,16,For in defence of each other.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/16
