OL,7,FAmaaz told the court when he was
OL,8,F'grabbed' by PC Marsden at a car park
OL,9,Fpay station he had not realised he was
OL,10,Fa police officer, and had resisted
OL,11,Farrest even when he saw the uniform
OL,12,Fbecause he feared the officer was
OL,13,F"going to batter him to death".
OL,15,FGiving evidence at the trial, P C
OL,16,FMarsden said he was unaware Amaaz had
OL,17,Fbeen tasered and he kicked him in the
OL,18,Fface "to stun the subject" as he
OL,19,Fbelieved he was attempting to get off
OL,20,Fthe floor.
