OL,7,FHe told the court he did not believe
OL,8,Fhe struck Amaaz's head with a stamp in
OL,9,Fwhich he sought to clamp down on the
OL,10,Floose wire of his police radio to
OL,11,Favoid it being used as a weapon
OL,12,Fagainst him.
OL,14,FAmaaz was convicted of the assault of
OL,15,FPC Lydia Ward causing actual bodily
OL,16,Fharm and the assault of emergency
OL,17,Fworker PC Ellie Cook.
OL,19,FHe was also found guilty of an earlier
OL,20,Fassault of a member of the public,
OL,21,FAbdulkareem Ismaeil, at the airport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/16
