OL,7,FThe jury - after 10 hours of
OL,8,Fdeliberating - was unable to reach
OL,9,Fverdicts on allegations that Amaaz and
OL,10,Fhis brother, Muhammad Ahmed, 26,
OL,11,Fassaulted PC Zachary Marsden causing
OL,12,Factual bodily harm.
OL,14,FThe Crown will seek a retrial on those
OL,15,Fcounts.
OL,17,FAamer Anwar, the solicitor for the
OL,18,Fbrothers, issued a brief statement
OL,19,Foutside court, with Amaad alongside
OL,20,Fhim.
